    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            57,
            132,
            146,
            147
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $\\left(0, \\frac{1}{4}\\right)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            154,
            241,
            183
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $F^{\\prime}(x) = 2 - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} = 0$ 得 $x = \\frac{1}{4}$ ，当 $0 < x < \\frac{1}{4}$ 时 $F^{\\prime}(x) < 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            190,
            710,
            222
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $F(x)$ 的单调减区间为 $\\left(0, \\frac{1}{4}\\right)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            233,
            371,
            258
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\left\\{0, \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{5}, \\frac{\\sqrt{15}}{5}\\right\\}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            269,
            311,
            301
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 旋转曲面方程为 $\\Sigma:3x^{2} + 2y^{2} + 3z^{2} = 12$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            307,
            504,
            322
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "法向量为 $n = \\{6x,4y,6z\\}_{(0,\\sqrt{3},\\sqrt{2})} = \\{0,4\\sqrt{3},6\\sqrt{2}\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            330,
            522,
            345
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所求的单位法向量为 $n^0 = \\left\\{0, \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{5}, \\frac{\\sqrt{15}}{5}\\right\\}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            355,
            458,
            384
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 $\\frac{2\\pi}{3}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            395,
            202,
            423
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $b_{3} = \\frac{1}{\\pi}\\int_{-\\pi}^{\\pi}f(x)\\sin 3x\\mathrm{d}x = 2\\int_{0}^{\\pi}x\\sin 3x\\mathrm{d}x$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            432,
            506,
            459
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= - \\frac {2}{3} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} x \\mathrm {d} (\\cos 3 x) = - \\frac {2}{3} x \\cos 3 x \\left| _ {0} ^ {\\pi} + \\frac {2}{3} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\cos 3 x \\mathrm {d} x = \\frac {2 \\pi}{3}. \\right.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            173,
            468,
            704,
            497
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            506,
            289,
            536
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\operatorname{grad} u = \\left\\{\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z}\\right\\} = \\left\\{\\frac{x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right\\},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            544,
            741,
            573
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $\\operatorname{div}(\\mathbf{grad} u) = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(\\frac{x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right) + \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial y}\\left(\\frac{y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right) + \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial z}\\left(\\frac{z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            582,
            739,
            611
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} = \\frac {y ^ {2} + z ^ {2} - x ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} + \\frac {x ^ {2} + z ^ {2} - y ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} + \\frac {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} - z ^ {2}}{\\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) ^ {2}} \\\\ = \\frac {1}{x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            216,
            618,
            690,
            688
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5)【答案】 $X = k(1,1,\\dots ,1)^{\\mathrm{T}}(k$ 为任意常数).",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            694,
            462,
            709
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $r(\\mathbf{A}) = n - 1$ ，所以 $\\mathbf{AX} = \\mathbf{0}$ 的基础解系含一个线性无关的解向量，又因为 $\\mathbf{A}\\left[ \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ 1\\\\ \\vdots \\\\ 1 \\end{array} \\right] = \\mathbf{0}$ ，所以 $\\mathbf{AX} = \\mathbf{0}$ 的通解为 $\\mathbf{X} = k(1,1,\\dots ,1)^{\\mathrm{T}}(k$ 为任意常数）.",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            715,
            741,
            814
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            59,
            820,
            148,
            835
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            840,
            206,
            856
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x)}{x^3} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\cos x\\cdot\\sin(\\sin^2x)}{3x^2} = \\frac{1}{3}$ 得 $f(x)\\sim \\frac{1}{3} x^{3}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            861,
            659,
            890
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又 $g(x)\\sim x^3$ ，故 $f(x)$ 是 $g(x)$ 的同阶但非等价的无穷小，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            899,
            657,
            914
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【答案】 （A）.",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            67,
            210,
            82
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 双纽线 $(x^{2} + y^{2})^{2} = x^{2} - y^{2}$ 的极坐标方程为 $r^2 = \\cos 2\\theta$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            87,
            646,
            103
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由对称性得双纽线所围成的面积为",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            110,
            378,
            125
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nA = 4 \\times \\frac {1}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{4}} \\cos 2 \\theta d \\theta = 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{4}} \\cos 2 \\theta d \\theta ,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            345,
            130,
            683,
            161
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "应选(A). ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            168,
            173,
            183
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            190,
            208,
            204
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 直线 $L_{1}$ 的方向向量为 $s_1 = \\{1, - 2,1\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            211,
            485,
            226
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "直线 $L_{2}$ 的方向向量为 $\\pmb{s}_2 = \\{1, - 1,0\\} \\times \\{0,2,1\\} = \\{-1, - 1,2\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            233,
            648,
            248
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设两直线的夹角为 $\\theta$ ，由 $\\cos \\theta = \\frac{|s_1 \\cdot s_2|}{|s_1| \\cdot |s_2|} = \\frac{1}{2}$ 得 $\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{3}$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            255,
            685,
            287
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 （B）.",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            293,
            206,
            308
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】令 $P(x,y) = [f(x) - \\mathrm{e}^x ]\\sin y$ ， $Q(x,y) = -f(x)\\cos y,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            315,
            661,
            331
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y}$ 得 $f^{\\prime}(x) + f(x) - \\mathrm{e}^{x} = 0$ ，即 $f^{\\prime}(x) + f(x) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            337,
            632,
            367
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $f(x) = \\left[\\int \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{\\int \\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right]\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int \\mathrm{d}x} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + C\\right)\\mathrm{e}^{-x},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            374,
            584,
            403
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $f(0) = 0$ 得 $C = -\\frac{1}{2}$ ，故 $f(x) = \\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - \\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{2}$ ，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            412,
            584,
            441
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            449,
            206,
            464
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $PQ = O$ 得 $r(P) + r(Q) \\leqslant 3$ ，当 $t \\neq 6$ 时 $r(Q) = 2$ ，则 $r(P) \\leqslant 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            470,
            723,
            486
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $\\pmb{P}$ 为非零矩阵得 $r(P)\\geqslant 1$ ，故 $r(P) = 1$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            491,
            545,
            506
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "三、",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            513,
            92,
            528
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】 $\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}}\\right)^{x} = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left\\{\\left[1 + \\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}} - 1\\right)\\right]^{\\frac{1}{\\sin{\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos{\\frac{1}{x}} - 1}}\\right\\} x\\cdot \\left(\\sin {\\frac{2}{x}} + \\cos {\\frac{1}{x}} - 1\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            535,
            855,
            576
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow \\infty} \\frac {\\sin \\frac {2}{x} + \\cos \\frac {1}{x} - 1}{\\frac {1}{x}}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\lim  _ {t \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin 2 t + \\cos t - 1}{t}} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {2}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            340,
            583,
            667,
            623
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【解】 方法一",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            629,
            214,
            644
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\int \\frac {x \\mathrm {e} ^ {x}}{\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}} \\mathrm {d} x = \\int \\frac {x \\mathrm {d} (\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1)}{\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}} = 2 \\int x \\mathrm {d} (\\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}) = 2 x \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - 2 \\int \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} \\mathrm {d} x,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            650,
            783,
            686
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = t$ ，即 $x = \\ln (1 + t^{2})$ ，则",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            695,
            409,
            712
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int \\sqrt {e ^ {x} - 1} d x = \\int t \\cdot \\frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t = 2 \\int \\left(1 - \\frac {1}{1 + t ^ {2}}\\right) d t = 2 t - 2 \\arctan t + C \\\\ = 2 \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - 2 \\arctan \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + C, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            719,
            685,
            775
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\int \\frac{x\\mathrm{e}^x}{\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1}}\\mathrm{d}x = (2x - 4)\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} +4\\arctan \\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} +C.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            782,
            605,
            816
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二 令 $\\sqrt{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = t$ ，则 $x = \\ln (1 + t^{2}),\\mathrm{d}x = \\frac{2t}{1 + t^{2}}\\mathrm{d}t,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            825,
            601,
            854
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int \\frac {x e ^ {x}}{\\sqrt {e ^ {x} - 1}} d x = \\int \\frac {\\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) \\cdot (1 + t ^ {2})}{t} \\cdot \\frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t \\\\ = 2 \\int \\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) d t = 2 t \\ln (1 + t ^ {2}) - 2 \\int \\frac {t \\cdot 2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} d t \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            861,
            592,
            933
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} = 2 t \\ln \\left(1 + t ^ {2}\\right) - 4 t + 4 \\arctan t + C \\\\ = (2 x - 4) \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + 4 \\arctan \\sqrt {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + C. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            210,
            71,
            584,
            107
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【解】 将方程 $x^{2}y^{\\prime} + xy = y^{2}$ 化为 $y^\\prime +\\frac{1}{x} y = \\frac{1}{x^2} y^2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            116,
            555,
            143
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $u = y^{-1}$ ，则 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}u}{\\mathrm{d}x} -\\frac{1}{x} u = -\\frac{1}{x^2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            152,
            373,
            181
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $u = \\left[\\int \\left(-\\frac{1}{x^2}\\right)\\mathrm{e}^{\\int -\\frac{1}{x}\\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right]\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -\\frac{1}{x}\\mathrm{d}x} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2x^2} +C\\right)x$ ，即 $\\frac{1}{y} = \\left(\\frac{1}{2x^2} +C\\right)x$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            186,
            776,
            219
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $y(1) = 1$ 得 $C = \\frac{1}{2}$ ，故满足条件的特解为 $y = \\frac{2x}{1 + x^2}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            226,
            572,
            255
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、【解】 由 $\\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} = \\sqrt{2 - x^2 - y^2}$ 得 $x^{2} + y^{2} = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            262,
            547,
            280
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "曲面 $\\Sigma$ 所围成的几何体 $\\Omega = \\{(x, y, z) \\mid x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 1, \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} \\leqslant z \\leqslant \\sqrt{2 - x^2 - y^2}\\}$ , 由高斯公式得",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            287,
            834,
            325
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\iint_ {z} 2 x z \\mathrm {d} y \\mathrm {d} z + y z \\mathrm {d} z \\mathrm {d} x - z ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iiint_ {\\Omega} (2 z + z - 2 z) \\mathrm {d} v = \\iiint_ {\\Omega} z \\mathrm {d} v \\\\ = \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} d x d y \\int_ {\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}}} ^ {\\sqrt {2 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}}} z d z = \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} (1 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}) d x d y \\\\ = \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} d \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {1} (r - r ^ {3}) d r = \\frac {\\pi}{2}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            331,
            828,
            438
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】 令 $S(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}(n^{2} - n + 1)x^{n}$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            448,
            413,
            481
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = 1$ 得级数 $\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}(n^{2} - n + 1)x^{n}$ 的收敛半径为 $R = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            484,
            626,
            517
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x = \\pm 1$ 时级数发散，故级数的收敛域为 $(-1,1)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            521,
            512,
            536
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $S(x) = \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}(n^{2} - n + 1)x^{n} = x^{2}\\sum_{n=2}^{\\infty}n(n - 1)x^{n - 2} + \\sum_{n=0}^{\\infty}x^{n}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            544,
            603,
            575
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= x ^ {2} \\left(\\sum_ {n = 2} ^ {\\infty} x ^ {n}\\right) ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\frac {1}{1 - x} = x ^ {2} \\left(\\frac {x ^ {2}}{1 - x}\\right) ^ {\\prime \\prime} + \\frac {1}{1 - x} = \\frac {1 - 2 x + 3 x ^ {2}}{(1 - x) ^ {3}},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
