        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}\\frac{(-1)^n(n^2 - n + 1)}{2^n} = S\\left(-\\frac{1}{2}\\right) = \\frac{22}{27}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            619,
