        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{6}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            92,
            190,
            121
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】设 $A_{1} = \\{$ 第一次取到正品 $\\}$ , $A_{2} = \\{$ 第一次取到次品 $\\}$ , $B = \\{$ 第二次取到次品 $\\}$ ,",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            127,
            789,
            143
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$P(A_{1}) = \\frac{10}{12},\\quad P(A_{2}) = \\frac{2}{12},\\quad P(B\\mid A_{1}) = \\frac{2}{11},\\quad P(B\\mid A_{2}) = \\frac{1}{11}$ ，则",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            149,
            688,
            179
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} P (B) = P \\left(A _ {1}\\right) P \\left(B \\mid A _ {1}\\right) + P \\left(A _ {2}\\right) P \\left(B \\mid A _ {2}\\right) \\\\ = \\frac {1 0}{1 2} \\times \\frac {2}{1 1} + \\frac {2}{1 2} \\times \\frac {1}{1 1} = \\frac {2}{1 2} = \\frac {1}{6}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            186,
            473,
            236
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll} \\frac{1}{4\\sqrt{y}}, & 0 < y < 4, \\\\ 0, & \\text{其他}. \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            47,
            244,
            334,
            298
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $F_{Y}(y) = P\\{Y \\leqslant y\\} = P\\{X^{2} \\leqslant y\\}$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            305,
            440,
            320
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $y < 0$ 时， $F_{Y}(y) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            327,
            289,
            341
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $y \\geqslant 4$ 时， $F_{Y}(y) = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            348,
            289,
            363
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $0 \\leqslant y < 4$ 时， $F_{Y}(y) = P\\{0 \\leqslant X \\leqslant \\sqrt{y}\\} = \\int_{0}^{\\sqrt{y}} \\frac{1}{2} \\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{\\sqrt{y}}{2}$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            80,
