            615,
            401
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "即 $F_{Y}(y) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}0, & y <   0,\\\\ \\frac{\\sqrt{y}}{2}, & 0\\leqslant y <   4,\\\\ 1, & y\\geqslant 4, \\end{array} \\right.$ 故 $f_{Y}(y) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}\\frac{1}{4\\sqrt{y}}, & 0 <   y <   4,\\\\ 0, & \\text{其他}. \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            409,
            632,
            486
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "十一、【解】 $(1)E(X) = \\int_{-\\infty}^{+\\infty}xf(x)\\mathrm{d}x = 0,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            47,
            491,
            413,
            518
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $E(X^2) = \\int_{-\\infty}^{+\\infty}x^2 f(x)\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_0^{+\\infty}x^2\\mathrm{e}^{-x}\\mathrm{d}x = \\Gamma (3) = 2$ ，得",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            525,
            582,
            551
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nD (X) = E \\left(X ^ {2}\\right) - [ E (X) ] ^ {2} = 2.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            558,
            371,
            576
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2) $\\operatorname{Cov}(X, |X|) = E(X|X) - E(X) \\cdot E(|X|)$ , ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            580,
            535,
            597
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $E(X|X|) = \\int_{-\\infty}^{+\\infty}x|x|f(x)\\mathrm{d}x = 0$ ，得 $\\operatorname {Cov}(X,|X|) = 0$ ，即 $X$ 与 $|X|$ 不相关.",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            603,
            785,
            630
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）设 $F(x,y)$ 为 $(X,|X|)$ 的联合分布函数，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            636,
            477,
            652
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nF (1, 1) = P \\{X \\leqslant 1, | X | \\leqslant 1 \\} = P \\{- 1 \\leqslant X \\leqslant 1 \\} = \\int_ {0} ^ {1} e ^ {- x} d x = 1 - \\frac {1}{e},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            658,
            716,
            686
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nF _ {X} (1) = P \\{X \\leqslant 1 \\} = \\frac {1}{2} \\int_ {- \\infty} ^ {1} e ^ {- | x |} d x = \\frac {1}{2} + \\frac {1}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {1} e ^ {- x} d x = 1 - \\frac {1}{2 e},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            695,
            665,
            723
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nF _ {| X |} (1) = P \\{| X | \\leqslant 1 \\} = \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- | x |} \\mathrm {d} x = 1 - \\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e}},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            92,
